@node History "History."

@{b}V1.00  - First public release.@{ub}

@{b}V1.10  - Second public release.@{ub}
       - Added choice to resize windows (or not).
       - Changed the four "Mode" buttons to a single cycle gadget.
       - Fixed a small oversight which caused the program to read the
         font prefs from the Workbench screen only. They are now read
         from whichever screen the program is opened on.

@{b}V1.20  -  V1.45  -  Internal and beta test versions.@{ub}
       - Thanks to Neil Hobbs <neil@kinega.demon.co.uk>
         for beta testing these new versions.

@{b}V1.46  - Third public release.@{ub}
       - Added menu items with keyboard shortcuts
       - Added tooltypes for all settings/prefs
       - Changed "Tile" behaviour to leave titlebar clear
       - Save settings/prefs option added in menu
       - Fixed a couple of Enforcer/Cyberguard hits (Doh!)

@{b}V1.47  - Small bug fix.@{ub}
       - Silly programmer error (forgot to include a menu flag :)
         (Thanks to Jacques Spaa for the report)

@endnode
